//  Header 
header
  nav
    .logo Kindergarten Admin
    .nav-links
      a(href="#features") Features
      a(href="#dashboard") Dashboard
      a(href="#contact") Contact
      a.login-btn(href="/login") Login
//  Hero Section 
section.hero
  .hero-content
    h1 Streamline Your Kindergarten Management
    p Our admin portal provides all the tools you need to efficiently manage children, staff, and daily operations in one centralized platform.
    .cta-buttons
      a.primary-btn(href="/login") Get Started
      a.secondary-btn(href="#features") Learn More
//  Features 
section.features#features
  .section-title
    h2 Admin Features
    p Powerful tools designed specifically for kindergarten administrators
  .features-grid
    .feature-card
      .feature-icon 👶
      h3 Child Management
      p Easily register and track all children in your care with detailed profiles and progress tracking.
    .feature-card
      .feature-icon 📊
      h3 Attendance Tracking
      p Automated daily attendance with reporting and analytics to monitor patterns.
    .feature-card
      .feature-icon 📝
      h3 Progress Reports
      p Create and share developmental progress reports with parents electronically.
    .feature-card
      .feature-icon 💰
      h3 Billing System
      p Automated tuition calculations, invoice generation, and payment tracking.
    .feature-card
      .feature-icon 📅
      h3 Event Calendar
      p Schedule and manage all kindergarten events and activities in one place.
    .feature-card
      .feature-icon 📱
      h3 Parent Communication
      p Integrated messaging system for seamless communication with parents.
